hopobject.body: I've only just arrived effexor 50 mg side effects The 507 lbs (230 kg) lithium-ion battery pack, made up of cells supplied by Sanyo, is mounted under the passenger cabin, giving the car a nice, stable, low center of gravity, nearly ideal 50/50 front-to-rear weight distribution, and a range BMW executives say will be between 80-100 miles (130-160km) per charge. The placement of the pack also lifts the passenger cabin off the pavement just enough to actually make it easier to get into and out of, a process simplified for the back seat passengers by the inclusion of a pair of rear-swinging 'suicide doors.'
